title: Laverne Cox on Trans Joy, Resistance & Survival | ICONIC INTERVIEW
description:
Olayemi Olurin interviewed Laverne Cox about her career,  navigating Hollywood as a trans woman, Orange Is The New Black, the rise of anti-trans legislation and rhetoric in the media, what advice she'd give her younger self and more!
